'''颱風奧馬'''（{{lang-en|Typhoon Omar}}），在菲律宾名为'''台风露西恩'''（{{lang-en|Typhoon Lusing}}）<ref name="adrc">{{cite report | archivedate = 2013-06-04 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130604045459/http://www.adrc.asia/publications/databook/ORG/databook_20th/PHL.pdf | url = http://www.adrc.asia/publications/databook/ORG/databook_20th/PHL.pdf | type = Dataset | page = 12 | title = Top 25 Natural Disasters in Philippines According to Number of Killed (1901–2000) | location = Kobe, Japan | publisher = Asian Disaster Reduction Center | year = 2003 | accessdate = 2015-09-21 | deadurl = no | format = [[PDF|PDF]]}}</ref>，是继1976年的[[1976年台风帕梅拉|台风帕梅拉]]以来吹袭[[关岛|关岛]]的最强[[台风|台风]]，也是对该岛造成破坏最严重的台风之一。系统源于1992年8月23日西[[太平洋|太平洋]]上空的大规模[[季风槽|季风槽]]，在向西移动的过程中缓慢强化成[[热带气旋|热带风暴]]，但因附近另一个热带气旋的影响而没有马上得以进一步增强。两场风暴间的距离拉开后，奥马尔迅速发展成强劲台风，于8月28日以[[最大持续风速|风力时速]]195公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]]关岛。次日，气旋达到最高强度，[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]估计其1分钟持续风速达到每小时240公里，属“[[超級台风|超級台风]]”标准{{#tag:ref|1分钟持续风速数据由美国在[[阿加尼亚|阿加尼亚]]设立的[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]提供<ref name="atcr">{{cite report | publisher = Joint Typhoon Warning Center | first1 = Donald A. | last1 = Mautner | first2 = Charles P. | last2 = Guard | year = 1992 | title = 1992 Annual Tropical Cyclone Report | series = [http://www.usno.navy.mil/JTWC/annual-tropical-cyclone-reports Annual Tropical Cyclone Reports] | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130221092211/http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/1992atcr.pdf | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2014-07-07 | url = http://www.usno.navy.mil/NOOC/nmfc-ph/RSS/jtwc/atcr/1992atcr.pdf | pages = 80–89 | location = Hagåtña, Guam | format = PDF | archivedate = 2013-02-21}}</ref>，10分钟持续风速数据则源自西太平洋[[区域专责气象中心|区域专责气象中心]][[气象厅_(日本)|日本气象厅]]<ref>{{cite web | publisher = World Meteorological Organization | date = n.d. | accessdate = 2015-09-21 | title = Latest Advisories on Current Tropical Cyclones Hurricanes Typhoons | work = Tropical Cyclone Programme | url = http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Advisories-RSMCs.html | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150606024426/http://www.wmo.int/pages/prog/www/tcp/Advisories-RSMCs.html | location = Geneva, Switzerland | archivedate = 2015-06-06}}</ref>。|group="注"}}。9月4日吹袭[[东台湾|台湾东部]]前，奥马尔有大幅减弱，次日再进入中华人民共和国东部上空，于9月9日逐渐消散。

奥马尔在关岛夺走1条人命，并造成4亿5700万美元的损失{{#tag:ref|所有损失数额均为1992年的货币数额。|group="注"}}。时速高达248公里的强烈阵风令全岛绝大多数区域停电数天之久。停电还令供水系统无法正常运作，联合台风警报中心在岛上的办事处连续11天无法发出灾害公告。岛上有2158套房屋受损或被毁，3000人无家可归。关岛的建筑法规从此提高标准，规定建筑物需要抵御时速250公里的狂风袭击，多家[[保险公司|保险公司]]也停止对那些不是采用混凝土建造的房屋提供新的保险政策。从菲律宾以北较远处海域经过期间，台风造成11人死亡，并对538套房屋造成价值9.03亿[[菲律宾披索|菲律宾披索]]（相当于3540万美元）的破坏。奥马尔接下来给日本南部岛屿带去狂风和小雨，该国农作物遭受了4.76亿[[日圆|日圆]]（相当于380万美元）的损失。气旋在台湾部分地区引发洪灾，导致3人遇难，经济损失约6500万美元，其中大部分都是农业损失。

== 气象历史 ==
{{storm path|Omar 1992 track.png}}
8月20日，西[[太平洋|太平洋]]开放水域上空出现[[热带扰动|热带扰动]]，并表现出[[对流|对流]]或[[雷暴|雷暴]]持续存在的迹象。在此期间，西太平洋盆地有两个[[热带气旋|热带气旋]]消散，还有一个转变成[[温带气旋|温带气旋]]，这使得西太平洋上空的[[季风槽|季风槽]]（西太平洋的大部分风暴都是由该季风槽催生出来）变得更有利于热带天气系统发展。<ref name="atcr" />据[[气象厅_(日本)|日本气象厅]]记载，之后发展成奥马尔的热带低气压是于[[协调世界时|协调世界时]]8月23日下午18点形成<ref name="jma">{{cite web | type = Database | publisher = [[气象厅_(日本)|Japan Meteorological Agency]] | date = 2014-06-02 | title = RSMC Best Track Data (1990–1999) | accessdate = 2014-11-02 | format = TXT | location = Tokyo, Japan | archivedate = 2014-11-02 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141102053515/http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/Besttracks/bst9099.txt | url = http://www.jma.go.jp/jma/jma-eng/jma-center/rsmc-hp-pub-eg/Besttracks/bst9099.txt}}</ref>。[[联合台风警报中心|联合台风警报中心]]估计系统的发展速度没有这么快，于{{lang|en|[[协调世界时|UTC]]}}当晚21点发布[[热带气旋形成警报|热带气旋形成警报]]，再于次日开始针对第15{{lang|en|W}}号热带低气压发布公告<ref name="atcr" />。

低气压总体向西移动，联合台风警报中心于8月25日将其升级成热带风暴<ref name="atcr" />，日本气象厅则在次日跟进<ref name="jma" />。气旋向西移动的速度开始减慢，其西侧不远处的[[1992年太平洋台风季|热带风暴波利]]在奥马尔上空产生强烈[[风切变|风切变]]，令其强化速度减缓。联合台风警报中心指出，风切变可能会使风暴的环流和对流分离，令其强度下滑。但随着奥马尔和波利之间的距离拉大，两个气旋间发展出[[高压脊|高压脊]]，奥马尔因此转向北上，再转朝[[罗盘方位|西北偏西]]方向飘移，并因行经洋面风切变减弱而得以继续增强。8月27日清晨，联合台风警报中心将奥马尔升级成台风，{{lang|en|UTC}}当晚23点左右，系统中开始呈现出[[风眼|风眼]]。<ref name="ncdc">{{cite journal |url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-4DE9ACF3-C99C-4CA7-AB11-A3D465B93ED9.pdf |title=Typhoon Omar strikes Guam on August 28, 1992 |first1=William |last1=Angel |first2=Greg |last2=Hammer |first3=Jay |last3=Hollifield |first4=Sharon |last4=Weaver |volume=34 |number=9 |date=1992-09 |ISSN=0039-1972 |journal=Storm Data and Unusual Weather Phenomena |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6XTcybGnz?url=http://www1.ncdc.noaa.gov/pub/orders/IPS/IPS-4DE9ACF3-C99C-4CA7-AB11-A3D465B93ED9.pdf |archivedate=2015-04-02 |pages=31–33 }}</ref>8月28日，奥马尔进入[[快速增强|快速增强期]]<ref name="atcr" />，日本气象厅也在这时将其归类为台风<ref name="jma" />。此后不久，风暴以[[最大持续风速|1分钟持续风速]]每小时195公里强度[[登陆_(气象学)|登陆]][[关岛|关岛]]<ref name="atcr" />，直径37公里的风眼<ref name="atcr" />从该岛北部缓慢经过，行进过程历时2.5小时<ref name="ncdc" />。

据日本气象厅估算，奥马尔于{{lang|en|UTC}}8月29日下午18点达到10分钟持续风速每小时185公里，最低[[气压|气压]]920[[巴|毫巴]]（[[帕斯卡|百帕]]，27.17[[英寸汞柱|英寸汞柱]]）的最高强度，台风在此强度下保持了24小时，然后开始逐渐减弱<ref name="jma" />。联合台风警报中心估计气旋的1分钟持续风速为每小时240公里，达到[[热带气旋风级|超級台风标准]]<ref name="atcr" />。两天后，台风进入[[菲律宾大气地球物理和天文服务管理局|菲律宾大气地球物理和天文服务管理局]]监控海域，该机构将风暴命名为“露西恩”（{{lang|en|Lusing}}）<ref name="adrc" />。到了{{lang|en|UTC}}9月3日下午15点，日本气象厅已把奥马尔降级成热带风暴<ref name="jma" />，但联合台风警报中心評估气旋直至次日都还有台风强度<ref name="atcr" />。风暴总体继续向西移动，于9月4日从[[花莲縣|花莲縣]][[秀姑巒溪|秀姑巒溪]]口登陆[[台湾|台湾]]东海岸<ref name="HKO" /><ref name="RDC28">{{cite web | archivedate = 2015-09-22 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150922151947/http://rdc28.cwb.gov.tw/TDB/ntdb/pageControl/typhoon?year=1992&num=199215&name=OMAR&from_warning=true | url = http://rdc28.cwb.gov.tw/TDB/ntdb/pageControl/typhoon?year=1992&num=199215&name=OMAR&from_warning=true | title = 歐馬颱風資料概況 | publisher = 交通部中央氣象局 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | location = 台北, 台湾 }}</ref><ref name="CWB1992">{{cite web | url = http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/rdcweb/lib/cd/cd02tyrp/tyr1992.exe | title = 民國八十一年颱風調查報告 | publisher = 交通部中央氣象局 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | format = EXE | archivedate = 2004-04-23 | location = 台北, 台湾 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20040423190420/http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/rdcweb/lib/cd/cd02tyrp/tyr1992.exe | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。奥马尔用了7小时穿越台湾，然后从[[云林县|云林县]]进入[[台湾海峡|台湾海峡]]<ref name="cwb">{{cite report | publisher = 中央氣象局 | title = 1992 年歐馬(OMAR)颱風 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/tyweb/tyfnweb/image/pdf-file/1992OMAR.pdf | work = Typhoon Data Bank | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411164140/http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/tyweb/tyfnweb/image/pdf-file/1992OMAR.pdf | location = 台北, 台湾 | year = 2009 | archivedate = 2015-04-11 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF }}</ref>。9月5日，风暴在经过台湾海峡后，先掠過[[福建省_(中華民國)|福建省]][[金門縣|金門縣]]，然後再從[[廈門市|廈門市]][[思明區|思明區]]附近登陆中华人民共和国东部<ref name="HKO">{{cite book | title = Tropical Cyclones in 1992 | url = http://www.hko.gov.hk/publica/tc/tc1992.pdf | publisher = Royal Observatory Hong Kong | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | location = 九龙, 香港 | pages = 14–15 | chapter = Section 2: Tropical Cyclone Overview for 1992 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20130930200121/http://www.hko.gov.hk/publica/tc/tc1992.pdf | date = 1994-09 | deadurl = no | id = 551.515.2:551.506.1(512.317) | archivedate = 2013-09-30}}</ref>。接下来奥马尔迅速減弱為热带低气压，然后转向西南偏西，在穿越中国南部期间繼續急剧弱化，于9月9日在[[越南|越南]]北部上空完全消散<ref name="jma" />。

== 防灾措施和影响 ==
[[File:Typhoon_Omar_Anigua_Guam.jpeg|thumb]]

=== 关岛 ===
风暴来袭前的8月25日，[[美国国防部|美国国防部]]下令关岛进入[[热带气旋警告|热带气旋三级警戒]]状态，该状态意指未来48小时内岛上可能遭遇破坏性风力袭击。1天后，关岛的警戒级别升为二级，除[[美国海军|美国海军]]的两艘舰船外，所有船只均驶离海港，以免受到台风破坏<ref name="navy" />，美国海军舰船则向关岛西南部进发，以期避开风暴<ref name="HeadsOfGuam" />。8月28日，岛上进入最高的一级警戒<ref name="navy">{{cite report | chapter = Section IV: Disaster Relief Operations | title = Command History 1992 | date = 1993-10-29 | publisher = Commander in Chief, United States Pacific Command; released to Nautilus Institute for Security and Sustainability under Freedom of Information Act requests | volume = 1 (unclassified) | location = Halawa, Hawaii | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | page = 163 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20140821230722/http://nautilus.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/1992.pdf | deadurl = no | url = http://nautilus.org/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/1992.pdf | archivedate = 2014-08-21 | format = PDF}}</ref>。关岛所有[[固定翼飞机|固定翼飞机]]和直升机全部挪入机库或转移到日本和菲律宾<ref name="HeadsOfGuam">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm heads for Guam | accessdate = 2014-07-08 | newspaper = The Free-Lance Star | agency = [[美联社|Associated Press]] | issue = 202 | date = 1992-08-26 | location = Fredericksburg, Virginia | page = A2 | volume = 108 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1298&dat=19920826&id=GvxNAAAAIBAJ&sjid=oIsDAAAAIBAJ&pg=4820,4317092&hl=zh-CN}}</ref>。奥马尔途经关岛期间，岛上所有学校均予关闭<ref name="CloserGuam">{{cite news | title = Tropical storm moves closer to Guam | date = 1992-08-26 | location = Hagåtña, Guam | agency = Associated Press | url = http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1992/Tropical-Storm-Moves-Closer-to-Guam-With-AM-Hurricane-Andrew-Bjt/id-d630c7f500e08db008334bc5f276797b | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archivedate = 2014-04-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150402174142/http://www.apnewsarchive.com/1992/Tropical-Storm-Moves-Closer-to-Guam-With-AM-Hurricane-Andrew-Bjt/id-d630c7f500e08db008334bc5f276797b}}</ref>。岛上的航班运作至少停止了两天<ref name="nyt">{{cite news | date = 1992-08-30 | title = After the storm: Thousands on Guam lose homes in typhoon | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150202195756/http://www.nytimes.com/1992/08/30/us/after-the-storm-thousands-on-guam-lose-homes-in-typhoon.html | newspaper = [[纽约时报|The New York Times]] | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | deadurl = no | url = http://www.nytimes.com/1992/08/30/us/after-the-storm-thousands-on-guam-lose-homes-in-typhoon.html | location = [[纽约|New York]], [[纽约州|New York]] | archivedate = 2015-02-02}}</ref>，导致5000名旅客滞留。风暴期间有约3100人躲进紧急避难所<ref name="ap831">{{cite news | newspaper = The Prescott Courier | location = Prescott, Arizona | agency = Associated Press | date = 1992-08-31 | title = Guam typhoon mop up begins | page = 2A | volume = 110 | issue = 200 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=886&dat=19920831&id=6KU0AAAAIBAJ&sjid=r30DAAAAIBAJ&pg=4277,7321777&hl=en}}</ref>。

奥马尔是[[1976年太平洋台风季|1976年]]的台风帕梅拉后吹袭关岛的最强台风，也是对该岛造成破坏最严重的台风之一<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="ncdc" />，岛上所有地区都能感受到这场风暴的威力<ref name="FederalAsst">{{cite news | title = Federal assistance to typhoon-stricken Guam | agency = PR Newswire | date = 1992-08-28 | location = New York, New York}}</ref>，热带风暴强度大风在岛上持续了16小时<ref name="atcr" />，气旋西侧风眼墙影响的部分地区阵风时速估计高达248公里<ref name="ncdc" />。风眼经过期间，狂风导致[[阿加尼亚|阿加尼亚]]的[[风速计|风速计]]失效，[[安德森空军基地|安德森空军基地]]的雷达也不见踪影<ref name="atcr" />，因此奥马尔在岛上产生的风速只有估算值，没有准确的测量值<ref name="navy" />。岛上以[[阿普拉港|阿普拉港]]气压最低，只有940毫巴（百帕，27.76英寸汞柱）。风暴缓慢的移动速度令岛上暴雨持续了很长时间，美国气象局驻关岛地方办事处测得的最高降雨量为519毫米，安德森空军基地也有417毫米<ref name="ncdc" /><ref name="WPCMAX">{{cite book | last = Roth | first = David M. | date = 2015-04-30 | chapter = Tropical Cyclone Point Maxima | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | location = College Park, Maryland | archivedate = 2015-07-02 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150702170533/http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | chapter-url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcmaxima.html | url = http://www.wpc.ncep.noaa.gov/tropical/rain/tcrainfall.html | publisher = Weather Prediction Center | title = Tropical Cyclone Rainfall Data}}</ref>。

关岛以中部地区到北海岸受灾最为严重，特别是旅游区和军事基地<ref name="ap829">{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | date = 1992-08-29 | newspaper = TimesDaily | location = Florence, Alabama | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | title = Guam hit hard by Typhoon Omar | page = 7A | volume = 123 | issue = 242 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1842&dat=19920829&id=4EoeAAAAIBAJ&sjid=GccEAAAAIBAJ&pg=4699,4198917&hl=en}}</ref><ref name="nyt" />。[[美国海军太平洋地区计算机和电信主工作站|美国海军计算机和电信主工作站]]因电力供应中断、同时发电机也因洪灾受损而不得不关闭<ref name="navy" />。美国海军[[尼加拉瓜瀑布号补给舰|尼加拉瓜瀑布号]]和[[怀特普莱恩斯号补给舰|怀特普莱恩斯号补给舰]]因遭遇狂风大浪而搁浅<ref name="dod">{{cite report | date = 1993-06-23 | url = http://www.gao.gov/assets/220/217920.pdf | location = Washington, D.C. | title = Disaster Assistance: DOD's Support for Hurricanes Andrew and Iniki and Typhoon Omar. Report to the Chairman, Subcommittee on Readiness, Committee on Armed Services, House of Representatives | publisher = United States General Accounting Office | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | docket = GAO/NSIAD-93-180 | archivedate = 2014-10-14 | deadurl = no | format = PDF | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141014021919/http://gao.gov/assets/220/217920.pdf}}</ref>，阿普拉港的[[旱坞|旱坞]]还被冲到岸上<ref name="navy" />。岛上数十家商店毁于一旦<ref name="ap920">{{cite news | newspaper = Star-News | agency = Associated Press | date = 1992-09-20 | title = A month after Typhoon Omar, residents of Guam rebuilding | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1454&dat=19920930&id=qohOAAAAIBAJ&sjid=sRQEAAAAIBAJ&pg=1272,5524785&hl=en | location = Wilmington, North Carolina | volume = 125 | issue = 302 | page = 8A}}</ref>。狂风令一架起重机倒在公寓楼上<ref>{{cite news | agency = Associated Press | title = Typhoon Omar pummels Guam | newspaper = The Telegraph | page = 20 | volume = 122 | issue = 446 | location = London, UK | date = 1992-08-28 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=2209&dat=19920828&id=qYlKAAAAIBAJ&sjid=AZQMAAAAIBAJ&pg=3911,5557621&hl=en}}</ref>，[[杜梦区|杜梦区]]有400根木制和20根混凝土制电线杆倒塌<ref name="atcr" />，导致全岛70%的区域停电<ref name="dod" />。关岛各地的交通和通讯受到严重扰乱，抽水系统也出现故障<ref name="atcr" />，山体滑坡导致道路被埋，低洼地区也被洪水淹没<ref name="nyt" />。岛上有约2000套民宅被毁，另外2200套受到不同程度破坏<ref name="ap831" />，近3000人流离失所<ref name="atcr" />。木制建筑物所受破坏最为严重，采用混凝土修建的楼房相对而言在风暴期间更加稳定可靠<ref name="navy" />。整个关岛一共遭受了4亿5700万美元损失<ref name="atcr" />，其中军事基地和民间遭受的损失数额基本持平<ref name="ap920" />。岛上有1人丧生<ref name="navy" />，200余人需要急救<ref name="atcr" />，其中约80人是被飞溅的瓦砾打伤<ref name="ap829" />。

=== 其它地区 ===
热带风暴波利在菲律宾引发洪灾和人员丧生仅数天后，奥马尔又在该国东北方向较远处洋面经过。菲律宾首席气象专家指出，奥马尔“比波利更强劲”，有可能“在大范围地区引发[[季风|季风]]降水”<ref>{{cite news | newspaper = New Straits Times | location = Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia | date = 1992-09-03 | title = Typhoon Omar roars closer to the Philippines | page = 23 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1309&dat=19920903&id=A5ZUAAAAIBAJ&sjid=HZADAAAAIBAJ&pg=6821,1021534&hl=en}}</ref>。最终台风实际影响的地区是[[吕宋|吕宋]]北部，主要包括[[科迪勒拉行政区|科迪勒拉行政区]]、[[伊罗戈|伊罗戈地区]]和[[卡加延河谷|卡加延河谷]]<ref name="php" />。气旋夺走菲律宾11条人命<ref name="adrc" />，还摧残了393套房屋，另有145套受损<ref name="php" />，该国1965人无家可归<ref name="adrc" />。估计整个菲律宾一共遭受了9.03亿[[菲律宾披索|菲律宾披索]]（相当于1992年的约3540万美元）的损失{{#tag:ref|来源中的损失数据为菲律宾披索，再用[[菲律宾中央银行|菲律宾中央银行]]提供的汇率换算成美元<ref>{{Cite web | location = Manila, Philippines | publisher = Bangko Sentral ng Pilipinas | title = Exchange Rates: Philippine Peso per US Dollar for 1992-2014 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | date = n.d. | url = http://www.bsp.gov.ph/dbank_reports/ExchangeRates_1_rpt.asp?frequency=Annual&range_from=1992&range_to=2014&conversion=Average}}</ref>。|group="注"}}，其中又以农业损失为主<ref name="php">{{cite web |publisher=National Disaster Coordinating Council |date=2004-11-09 |accessdate=2015-09-22 |title=Destructive Typhoons 1970-2003 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150704023652/http://baseportal.com/cgi-bin/baseportal.pl?htx=%2Fmiso%2Ftyphoons&range=120%2C20 |url=http://baseportal.com/cgi-bin/baseportal.pl?htx=/miso/typhoons&range=120,20 |at=entries 121–140 |type=Dataset |location=Quezon City, Philippines |archivedate=2015-07-04 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>。

离开关岛后，奥马尔以风力时速78公里强度吹袭[[臺中縣|臺中縣]][[梧栖区|梧棲鎮]]<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="sum">{{cite report | publisher = 交通部中央氣象局 | location = 台北, 台湾 | work = 侵臺颱風資料庫 | title = 本颱風摘要 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150411165952/http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/tyweb/tyfnweb/htm/explanation-1992omar.htm | date = 2011-08-05 | accessdate = 2015-04-06 | url = http://photino.cwb.gov.tw/tyweb/tyfnweb/htm/explanation-1992omar.htm | archivedate = 2015-04-11 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。大范围降水给岛上造成的影响最为严重，降雨量最大的地区集中在台湾南部，[[高雄市_(1979年-2010年)|高雄市]]的降雨量达到最高的375.4毫米<ref name="cwb" /><ref name="sum" />。台湾有5个[[县_(台湾)|县]]爆发洪灾，共76万6000人失去供电。高雄市有4艘船被大浪冲到岸上<ref name="HKO" />，高雄市、[[高雄縣|高雄縣]]、云林县、[[嘉義縣|嘉義縣]]和[[屏东县|屏东县]]的农业和渔业均受重创<ref name="cwb" />。全臺共有3人死亡（其中2人溺斃）、12人受伤，经济损失超过6500万美元<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="sum" />。

奥马尔的边缘[[雨带|雨带]]在[[日本|日本]]外围多个岛屿产生小雨，降雨量最高的[[西表岛|西表岛]]为28毫米，阵风时速则以[[与那国岛|与那国岛]]最高，达到72公里<ref>{{cite report | work = Digital Typhoon | publisher = National Institute of Informatics | archiveurl = http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/dsummary.pl?id=199215&basin=wnp&lang=en | location = Tokyo, Japan | date = n.d. | title = Typhoon 199215 (Omar) | url = http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/dsummary.pl?id=199215&basin=wnp&lang=en | deadurl = no | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archivedate = 2015-04-04}}</ref>。日本南部多个岛屿上的甘蔗和秋葵作物受到气旋破坏，农作物损失总额达4亿7600万[[日圆|日圆]]（相当于约380万美元）{{#tag:ref|来源中的损失数据为[[日圆|日圆]]，再用{{lang|en|Oanda Corporation}}网站提供的汇率换算成美元<ref name="oanda">{{cite web | publisher = Oanda Corporation | date = n.d. | title = 历史汇率 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = http://www.oanda.com/lang/cns/currency/historical-rates/ | type = Database | location = Toronto, Canada}}</ref>。|group="注"|name="jpy"}}。该国交通也受到扰乱，38架次航班取消<ref>{{cite report|work=Digital Typhoon |publisher=National Institute of Informatics |location=Tokyo, Japan |title=Weather Disaster Report (1992-918-05) |accessdate=2015-09-22 |archiveurl=https://archive.is/20150404121648/http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=1992-918-05&lang=en |deadurl=no |url=http://agora.ex.nii.ac.jp/cgi-bin/dt/report.pl?id=1992-918-05&lang=en |archivedate=2015-04-04 }}</ref>。此后，奥马尔还在经过中华人民共和国南部期间给沿途地区带去降水，[[香港|香港]]西北部部分地区于9月7日出现洪灾<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="HKO" />。

== 善后 ==
[[File:Typhoon_Omar.JPG|right]]

风暴登陆关岛后，[[关岛总督|前总督]][[约瑟夫·富兰克林·阿达|约瑟夫·富兰克林·阿达]]（{{lang|en|Joseph Franklin Ada}}）宣布全岛进入[[紧急状态|紧急状态]]<ref>{{cite news | title = Typhoon Omar devastates Guam | newspaper = The Spokesman-Review | page = A3 | volume = 6 | issue = 95 | edition = State | location = Spokane, Washington | date = 1992-08-29 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | url = https://news.google.com/newspapers?nid=1314&dat=19920829&id=JHUzAAAAIBAJ&sjid=OfADAAAAIBAJ&pg=4808,6389574&hl=en}}</ref>，[[美国总统|前总统]][[乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什|乔治·赫伯特·沃克·布什]]宣布关岛为联邦灾区<ref name="GuamDisaster">{{cite news | title = Bush declares Guam federal disaster area | agency = [[合众国际社|United Press International]] | date = 1992-08-28 | location = [[哥伦比亚特区|Washington, D.C.]]}}</ref>。气旋过去后，岛上多人因抢劫被捕<ref name="ap829" />。[[联邦紧急事务管理局|联邦紧急事务管理局]]开设多个灾难援助中心，方便居民申请联邦援助，最终提供的援助款数额约为1840万美元，其中包括灾害住房、风暴相关的失业救济金，以及向家庭或商户提供的赠款<ref name="weri" />，超过1万1000人因此受益<ref name="ap920" />。[[美国联邦政府|联邦政府]]通常会承担地方灾害75%的救灾和清理开销，但这次岛上的杂物清理、应急工作，以及未投保公共建筑的重建均100%由联邦政府出资。这主要是因为美国在短短3周里连续受到3个强烈的热带气旋袭击，除奥马尔外，[[佛罗里达州|佛罗里达州]]与[[夏威夷州|夏威夷州]]还分别于这年8月和9月受到[[飓风安德鲁|飓风安德鲁]]和[[飓风伊尼基|飓风伊尼基]]的摧残。国防部派出27名[[关岛国民警卫队|关岛国民警卫队员]]和700名军人前往灾区提供援助。[[美国军方|军方]]提供了价值575万美元的临时住房、发电机和建筑物资，不过大部分救灾资源还是由政府提供。<ref name="dod" />当地[[国际红十字与红新月运动|红十字会]]在风暴过后提供了600万美元救助金<ref name="weri">{{cite report | year = 1999 | title = Typhoon Vulnerability Study for Guam | first1 = Charles | last1 = Guard | first2 = Michael | last2 = Hamnett | first3 = Charles | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20121024010432/http://www.weriguam.org/docs/reports/85_8.pdf | last3 = Newmann | first4 = Mark | last4 = Lander | first5 = H. Galt Jr. | last5 = Siegrist | location = Mangilao, Guam | publisher = Water and Environmental Research Institute of the Western Pacific | url = http://www.weriguam.org/docs/reports/85_8.pdf | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archivedate = 2012-10-24 | deadurl = yes }}</ref>。面对安德鲁、伊尼基和奥马尔的连串沉重打击，[[美国国会|联邦国会]]通过1992年紧急补充拨款法案，通过9月30日结束的财政年度向救灾机构提供更多资金<ref>{{cite act | type = Bill | number = H.R.5620 | articletype = Title | article = II: Department of Defense – Military | publisher = 102nd Congress of the United States of America (1991–1992) | title = Dire Emergency Supplemental Appropriations Act, 1992, Including Disaster Assistance To Meet the Present Emergencies Arising From the Consequences of Hurricane Andrew, Typhoon Omar, Hurricane Iniki, and Other Natural Disasters, and Additional Assistance to Distressed Communities | date = 1992-09-23 | location = Washington, D.C. | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150407171835/https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/102/hr5620/text | deadurl = no | archivedate = 2015-04-07 | url = https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/102/hr5620/text }} {{Wayback|url=https://www.govtrack.us/congress/bills/102/hr5620/text |date=20150407171835 }}</ref>。

联合台风警报中心驻关岛办事处连续11天无法运作，其预警职责只能由后备机构承担。机场雷达所受破坏促使高分辨率气象雷达网络{{lang|en|[[NEXRAD|NEXRAD]]}}（意为“下一代雷达”）于1993年2月提前安装<ref name="atcr" />，岛上航班的起飞和降落都局限在白天进行<ref name="ap831" />。8月30日，一艘海军船只停靠在阿普拉港，提供临时移动雷达。到9月15日时，被冲到岸上的两艘船均已重新下水。<ref name="navy" />多家保险公司在灾后决定，停止向不是用混凝土修筑的建筑物提供新保险政策<ref name="weri" />。1996年1月，前总督[[卡尔·古铁雷斯|卡尔·古铁雷斯]]（{{lang|en|Carl Gutierrez}}）发布行政命令，要求岛上的住宅和[[飓风百叶窗|风暴百叶窗]]都至少要能够抵御时速250公里的狂风吹袭<ref>{{cite report | first = Carl | last = Gutierrez | title = Executive Order No. 96-01 | publisher = Officer of the Governor of the Territory of Guam | date = 1996-01-11 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150922140928/http://documents.guam.gov/wp-content/uploads/E.O.-96-01-Relative-to-Establishing-A-Minimum-Basic-Windloa.pdf | archivedate = 2015-09-22 | deadurl = yes | format = PDF | url = http://documents.guam.gov/wp-content/uploads/E.O.-96-01-Relative-to-Establishing-A-Minimum-Basic-Windloa.pdf }}</ref>。

因奥马尔导致流离失所的居民暂时住在人称奥马尔营的[[帐篷区|帐篷区]]，上千人擠在约200顶帐篷中<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="ap920" />。志愿者和军方花了数周时间清理岛上大部分垃圾<ref name="atcr" />。许多重要道路在气旋过去3天后就已恢复通行<ref name="ap831" />。岛上的供水预计在风暴过去几天内就能恢复<ref name="ap831" />，但供电却是在4周后才全面恢复，学校和商户因此受到影响<ref name="grieger">{{cite journal | title = Acute stress disorder, subsequent posttraumatic stress disorder and depression after a series of typhoons | pmid = 9160626 | journal = Anxiety | url = http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9160626 | doi = 10.1002/(SICI)1522-7154(1996)2:5<219::AID-ANXI3>3.0.CO;2-H | volume = 2 | issue = 5 | year = 1996 | pages = 219–225 | first1 = Jeffrey P. | last1 = Staab | first2 = Thomas A. | last2 = Grieger | first3 = Carol S. | last3 = Fullerton | first4 = Robert J. | last4 = Ursano | archivedate = 2015-09-22 | deadurl = no | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150922141804/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9160626}}</ref>。学校于9月14日重新开放<ref name="navy" />，大部分商户在月底恢复运营<ref name="ap920" />。美国军方于9月19日中止救灾工作<ref name="navy" />，但由于之后又有数场台风过境，岛上的完全恢复尚需时日。由于奥马尔已经摧毁了岛上许多较为脆弱的建筑物，因此之后来袭风暴造成的破坏程度低于正常水平。不过，这也导致奥马尔和同年12月[[1992年台风盖伊|台风盖伊]]产生的破坏难以区分。<ref name="ncdc" />1993年，医学杂志《焦虑》（{{lang|en|''Anxiety''}}）经抽样调查发现，320名受到奥马尔影响的灾民中有7.2%患上[[急性应激障碍|急性应激障碍]]，还有15%出现创伤后应激障碍的早期症状，这其中又以经历过之后台风的参与者占比最高。约5.9%的参与者表现出[[创伤后心理压力紧张症候群|创伤后应激障碍]]症状，这一比例和1989年[[飓风雨果|飓风雨果]]引发的情形类似。<ref name="grieger" />

台风奥马尔对关岛构成重创，其名称因此于1993年退役，由“奥斯卡”（{{lang|en|Oscar}}）取代<ref name="atcr" /><ref name="TCRR">{{cite journal | first1 = Xiaotu | last1 = Lei | first2 = Xiao | last2 = Zhou | journal = Tropical Cyclone Research And Review | volume = 1 | issue = 1 | doi = 10.6057/2012TCRR01.03 | date = 2012-02 | title = Summary of retired typhoons within the western North Pacific Ocean | pages = 23–32 | url = http://tcrr.typhoon.gov.cn/cn/Y2012/V1/I1/23 | accessdate = 2015-09-22 | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20150922141232/http://tcrr.typhoon.gov.cn/cn/Y2012/V1/I1/23 | deadurl = yes | archivedate = 2015-09-22 | author =  }}</ref>。

